Hi yan y,
It is now the 13th January and my last email was the 6th January. I would really appreciate if you could reply to my emails or forward them on to a staff member as you mentioned would happen so they could get back to me to clear this matter up quickly. I need to know when i will receive my product i purchased on the 10th December for a Xmas presents and to date i still have note received my Smart Nightable which i paid for and never received a confirmation email of purchase or any notification that my items has been sent. Also there is no tracking to know when my item will arrive. i had a very disappointed and unhappy son when there was no present to give to him at Xmas under the tree. I would like this matter attended to urgently and a reply please. I paid $242.62 for this item which is a lot of money to me and would like a refund or item sent please.

Regards Robyn
   ----- Forwarded message ----- From: Mrs De George <funkydotfood@yahoo.com.au>To: yan y <support@zakmma.com>Sent: Sunday, 6 January 2019, 7:04:14 pm AESTSubject: Fw: URGENT smart nightable Australia
  yan y
It has been another 27 days since i had sent my last email in regards to replying to you email to me promising i would be contacted by a staff member promptly re my product. I have for filled my request of information you needed and todate have not had any reply. I would like to know what is going on with my order i placed back in end of November 2018. When will i receive my product that i have paid for and that money was taken from my account 2 day after purchase with no tracking available to know where my smart night table is. This is an urgent inquiry that i need an answer to. If i don't get an answer and product within the next few weeks i will black list your company any way i can so others will not have the same dealings that i have experienced being ripped off by a false product that i was never going to receive.
Regards Robyn De George
   ----- Forwarded message ----- From: funkydotfood <funkydotfood@yahoo.com.au>To: yan y <support@zakmma.com>Sent: Monday, 10 December 2018, 11:19:29 pm AESTSubject: URGENT smart nightable Australia
 Hi yan yI purchased a smart night table online with purchase price of $169.99 for a Xmas present. After confirmation of purchasing it mentioned it may cost more money than advertised with the converson to Australia which it didnt mention any of this prior to confirming purchase and at no point did it tell me how much would be taken from my account. I purchased this on the 24th November and on the 26th November $242.62 was taken from my account.
I did receive a message with a massive code which i couldn't bring up to get the invoice number or proof of purchase (below was texted to me). Also on cofirmation it didnt tell me when it would arrive to my address. There was no tracking available so i dont know if i will even get my product by Xmas with only 14 days to go.
I am very disappointed and did wonder if i had been scamed as it has taken 17 days to get a response to my inquiry i loged on day of purchase on the 24th November. I would like to know why there was no information prior to final purchase on cost with converson rate. As i would not have purchased the product. There was no clear proof of purchase and not supplied with tracking to what date expected to arrive at my address in Australia plus what courier company would be delivering my smart nightable so i could contact them to see where my package was.
At this stage I dont have confidence i will get my product in time for Xmas.Has it left your warehouse?, is it in Australia. All urgent question i need urgently addressed.
My email address below on purchase and you have contacted me so you have my email so im not sure why you want it again.funkydotfood@yahoo.com.auName: Robyn De GeorgeAddress: 11 Hope Street Bundaberg West 4670 Qld Australia
I would like answeres to my questions and formost when will i get the product i order online?????This is an urgent inquiryRegards Robyn

Dear Sir

On 16th November 2018 I ordered an Electric scooter from your website. 
It cost $159.99 USD.

The money has been taken from my credit card but to date I have not 
received the goods.

I was sent a tracking number but when I checked it it was for a parcel 
which had been delivered in Switzerland, I am in New Zealand.  It also 
said it had been posted through a pigeon hole which I am sure you can 
see would be impossible for an electric scooter.

Please can you check on this situation for me and let me know when I can 
expect the scooter.  It is no longer on your website so if you have no 
further stock I would appreciate a refund of the money paid.

Thank you


Murray Holland

Hi yan yI purchased a smart night table online with purchase price of $169.99 for a Xmas present. After confirmation of purchasing it mentioned it may cost more money than advertised with the converson to Australia which it didnt mention any of this prior to confirming purchase and at no point did it tell me how much would be taken from my account. I purchased this on the 24th November and on the 26th November $242.62 was taken from my account.
I did receive a message with a massive code which i couldn't bring up to get the invoice number or proof of purchase (below was texted to me). Also on cofirmation it didnt tell me when it would arrive to my address. There was no tracking available so i dont know if i will even get my product by Xmas with only 14 days to go.
I am very disappointed and did wonder if i had been scamed as it has taken 17 days to get a response to my inquiry i loged on day of purchase on the 24th November. I would like to know why there was no information prior to final purchase on cost with converson rate. As i would not have purchased the product. There was no clear proof of purchase and not supplied with tracking to what date expected to arrive at my address in Australia plus what courier company would be delivering my smart nightable so i could contact them to see where my package was.
At this stage I dont have confidence i will get my product in time for Xmas.Has it left your warehouse?, is it in Australia. All urgent question i need urgently addressed.
My email address below on purchase and you have contacted me so you have my email so im not sure why you want it again.funkydotfood@yahoo.com.auName: Robyn De GeorgeAddress: 11 Hope Street Bundaberg West 4670 Qld Australia
I would like answeres to my questions and formost when will i get the product i order online?????This is an urgent inquiryRegards Robyn

column6: Отправлено с телефона Huawei

Hi,

Thank you for your order and we are extremely sorry for the late reply.

Our shipping team has shipped your order and a shipping confirmation email was sent you as well.

**Here is our General Delivery Timelines:**

* Jewelry and other items (Within US Delivery)– please allow 4 to 6 weeks from the date you place your order
* Jewelry and other items (Shipped Internationally)– please allow up to 4 to 6 weeks from the date you place your order

Your shipping confirmation email was sent to the email address you have provided when you place your order. Sometimes, the email may go directly to your SPAM folder depending on your email settings.

**Tracking Numbers**

* Because of the issue with the tracking information not updating timely, we will not be providing tracking numbers for non apparel-related orders until further notice.
* Regardless of the issues with the updating of tracking numbers, your orders are still shipped and delivered as expected based on the timelines provided above. We stand behind our products and will take good care of you.

Thank you so much for your business and patience. Let us know if you need anything else.

Kind Regards,
Mickey
Wanderland Designs Team

https://www.facebook.com/misssimpatiaofficial



And here’s one of my music videos (if you see it I’ll be honored!)

https://www.facebook.com/misssimpatiaofficial/videos/10154187430208683/



Moreover, I’ve 34k Instagram followers and an average of 1k likes per pic.

 https://www.instagram.com/sandrapiace/



On Youtube my videos account 10 MILLION visuals at all, my personal channel
2 MILLION.



Why am I writing all of this to you?

Because, beneath the music, I’m concerned with social marketing for public
figures, brands and companies.

I’d like to start a collaboration in terms of product placement, totally
free, with you.

I’d love to wear your dresses in my next photo session and videoclips,
tagging you and all your social pages in my media, as obvious.

I can also write a review of your brand on my official site
www.sandrapiace.it



I shall help you in the management of your social pages, discovering the
algorithms behind them.

Or else I’ll explain to you how to grow your followers to 30k, 50k or more,
planning a strategy to repeat in order to reach your customers and keep
their loyalty in time… and gaining new ones, of course!

10 million visuals, 600k likes, 30k shared contents, these are some of the
numbers I achieved in my social pages.

But in the last year I started also 40 viral campaign made for brands
(make-up, accessories and clothing), companies, events and public figures.

My best business card are my results: some posts of mine has reached 100k
likes, 20k shares and 7k comments with NO SPONSORSHIP OR PROMOTION.

Usually who concerns about marketing doesn’t manage to get these goals but
I follow a project until I reach the target on schedule.

The key is truly simple.

I love my job and I know how the algorithms work.

For a privacy matter I can’t show you what I do for the other brands, but
clicking here you can see an Instagram page I created just to demonstrate I
score these numbers not only on my pages, but everywhere else:



https://www.instagram.com/migliori_stati_di_whatsapp/



I don’t make links but relationships and emotions, I love to know who stays
behind a brand, their dreams, their expectations.

I love to guide people to their personal success.

In a world full of smilies and emoticons I like to smile live.





Notes about me:



I studied lyrical singing for 10 years, I love hiphop culture so much it
brought me to exhibit in Mexico in 2016. Why? To celebrate the 50th
birthday of VANS on the main stage, guesting Cappadonna from Wu Tang Clan!

From the very first years I expressed my love to work in the field of art
and communication, when I was 15 I’ve directed a tv spot for Sprite that
had been broadcasted on MTV.

I was the main character of the spot.

They chose my plot in a plenty of 10k candidates.

That moment is when I knew what I should do in my entire life (in addition
to save the world dressed as a super-heroine, but then I reflected upon
that and it seemed not to be a good idea).

On 21 I signed my first contract with Sony.

In 2007 I lent my voice to the spot Nike made for the FIFA World Cup just
when Italy won it!

I made a lot of things in my life and I done all of them with deep love.

I don’t like to lose and this is the way I face every viral campaign I set.

It becomes my mission.

I’m headstrong and I don’t surrender!



Long story short:

I’d like to receive 5-6 pieces I love from your collection to follow you
for about 6-10 months.

During this period I’m going to make your social grow and your follower
rise, showing how to become a web juggernaut!



I leave you my technical file even if it isn’t upgraded, just to give you
an idea about the press and the tv shows I’ve appeared in.



https://www.dropbox.com/s/b1w7kil8vl60hov/Sandra%20Piace%20Bio.pdf?dl=0



With love,

Sandra

Refund Policy
Refund Policy



----



Returns

The products can be returned or exchanged within 14 days after received



Customers will only be charged once for shipping costs (this includes
returns); No-restocking to be charged to the consumers for the return of
the product.

To be eligible for a return, your item must be unused and in the same
condition that you received it. It must also be in the original packaging.

To complete your return, we require a receipt or proof of purchase.

Please do not send your purchase back to the manufacturer.



Refunds (if applicable)

Once your return is received and inspected, we will send you an email to
notify you that we have received your returned item. We will also notify
you of the approval or rejection of your refund.

If you are approved, then your refund will be processed, and a credit will
automatically be applied to your credit card or original method of payment,
within a certain amount of days.



Late or missing refunds (if applicable)

If you haven’t received a refund yet, first check your bank account again.

Then contact your credit card company, it may take some time before your
refund is officially posted.

Next contact your bank. There is often some processing time before a refund
is posted.

If you’ve done all of this and you still have not received your refund yet,
please contact us at support@zakmma.com.





Exchanges (if applicable)

We only replace items if they are defective or damaged.  If you need to
exchange it for the same item, send us an email at

support@zakmma.com





Shipping

To return your product, you should mail your product to: Address: Room
1501,Grand Millennium Plaza(Lower Block), 181 Queen's Road Central, Hong
Kong.



Depending on where you live, the time it may take for your exchanged
product to reach you, may vary.



If you are shipping an item over $75, you should consider using a trackable
shipping service or purchasing shipping insurance. We don’t guarantee that
we will receive your returned item.


Politique de remboursement
Politique de remboursement

----

Résultats

Les produits peuvent être retournés ou échangés dans les 14 jours après
réception

Les clients ne seront facturés qu’une fois pour les frais d’expédition (ce
qui inclut les retours); Pas de réapprovisionnement à facturer aux
consommateurs pour le retour du produit.

Pour être éligible à un retour, votre article doit être inutilisé et dans
le même état que vous l'avez reçu. Il doit également être dans l'emballage
d'origine.

Pour compléter votre retour, nous avons besoin d’un reçu ou d’une preuve
d’achat.

Veuillez ne pas renvoyer votre achat au fabricant.

Remboursements (si applicable)

Une fois que votre retour est reçu et inspecté, nous vous enverrons un
courrier électronique pour vous informer que nous avons reçu votre article
retourné. Nous vous informerons également de l'approbation ou du rejet de
votre remboursement.

Si votre demande est approuvée, votre remboursement sera traité et un
crédit sera automatiquement appliqué à votre carte de crédit ou à votre
mode de paiement initial, dans un délai donné.

Remboursement tardif ou manquant (si en vigueur)

 Si vous n’avez pas encore reçu de remboursement, vérifiez d’abord votre
compte bancaire.

 Ensuite, contactez votre compagnie de carte de crédit, cela peut prendre
un certain temps avant que votre remboursement soit officiellement publié.

 Ensuite, contactez votre banque. Il y a souvent un peu de temps de
traitement avant qu'un remboursement soit posté.

 Si vous avez déjà fait tout cela et que vous n’avez toujours pas reçu
votre remboursement, veuillez nous contacter à support@zakmma.com.

 Échanges (si applicable)

 Nous ne remplaçons que les articles défectueux ou endommagés. Si vous avez
besoin de l'échanger pour le même article, envoyez-nous un email à

 support@zakmma.com

 livraison

 Pour renvoyer votre produit, vous devez l’envoyer à l’adresse suivante:
Adresse: Salle 1501, Grand Millennium Plaza (bâtiment inférieur), 181
Queen's Road Central, Hong Kong.

 En fonction de votre lieu de résidence, le temps nécessaire pour que votre
produit échangé vous parvienne peut varier.

 Si vous expédiez un article de plus de 75 $, vous devriez envisager
d’utiliser un service d’expédition suivi ou de souscrire une assurance
expédition. Nous ne garantissons pas que nous allons recevoir votre article
retourné.

On 11 December 2018, our Charity Committee is holding a quiz and raffle at The Sir Christopher Hatton Pub in Holborn with all proceeds raised being donated to our charity of the year, CALM - Campaign Against Living Miserably (https://www.thecalmzone.net/ ). CALM's work focuses on male suicide - the single biggest killer of men aged under 45 in the UK.

I was hoping that you might consider donating an item or two, to include as a prize in our raffle. Should you donate, we will ensure you are thanked on the evening and that your logo appears on the event's literature.

Attendees on the night will be in the region of 80-100 people and will include solicitors, barristers, our business partners and members of the wider London legal community. We have held this event each year for the last few years and are confident of its ever growing success.

Should you have any questions or require further information please do not hesitate to contact me.

I look forward to hearing from you.

Yours faithfully,
Venus Masiha
Child Care Paralegal

[Hanne & Co]<http://www.hanne.co.uk/>
